Text: After installation and reboot I start the app, says it needs to download something, it jumps from 1% directly to 92% and then does nothing. If I disable the wi-fi the program immediatly asks for retry or cancel,  so I know it isnt stuck. I have waited for as long as 30 minutes. Any ideas what im doing wrong?

Never mind. I guess i just needed to wait a little longer. The app works great in my Asus TF700. Just be patient while updating. Maps are huge, thats why it takes a while to update. Thank you for sharing this.
